Package: BLOOM
Type: Package
Title: BLOOM: Bulk and singLe-cell transcriptOmics integration for phenOtype-attributable cell subtype Mapping in plants
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jie Hao, Xin Zou, Anzhuo Zhang, Fulan Deng
Maintainer: Jie Hao <jhao@cemps.ac.cn>
Description: A computational framework that transfers phenotype-associated signals from bulk RNA-seq to the single-cell level, using partial least squares to achieve robust interpretation in limited-sample plant datasets.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), Seurat, pls, MASS, ggplot2, readxl, tcltk
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
NeedsCompilation: no
